ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectCanada-Korea - Agreement for Science, Technology and Innovation Cooperation
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, or to delegate authority to sign, on behalf of the Government of Canada, subject to ratification, the AGREEMENT FOR SCIENCE, TECHNOLOGY AND INNOVATION COOPERATION between the Government of Canada and the Government of the REPUBLIC OF KOREA.
